<br>
<strong>REFERENCE LIST ENTRY</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a reference list at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	Author(s) of chapter. (Year of publication). Title of chapter. In Editor(s) (Ed[s].), 
	<em>Title of book</em> (pages of the chapter referred to). Place of publication: Publisher.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Examples</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Author(s) of chapter">Smith, A.</span> 
	(<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2056</span>). 
	<span class="hover" title="Title of chapter">Synthetic reactions and strategies</span>. In 
	<span class="hover" title="Editor(s)">B. A. Brown</span> (Ed.),  
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of book">Principles of organic chemistry</span></em> 
	(<span class="hover" title="pages of the chapter referred to">pp. 123&#45;147</span>). 
	<span class="hover" title="Place of publication">Washington, DC</span>:  
	<span class="hover" title="Publisher">Wilton</span>.
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Author(s) of chapter">Smith, A., &amp; Brown, B.</span> 
	(<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2056</span>). 
	<span class="hover" title="Title of chapter">Natural reactions and strategies</span>. In 
	<span class="hover" title="Editor(s)">B. A. Brown &amp; C. Chan</span> (Eds.), 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of book">Principles of biology</span></em> 
	(<span class="hover" title="pages of the chapter referred to">pp. 148&#45;189</span>). 
	<span class="hover" title="Place of publication">Washington, DC</span>: 
	<span class="hover" title="Publisher">Wilton</span>.
</blockquote>
<br>
For a numbered edition, place the abbreviation in parenthesis after the book title. This part 
should not be italicised. Use (Rev. ed.) for revised editions.
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	<span class="hover" title="Author(s) of chapter">Smith, A., &amp; Brown, B.</span> 
	(<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2056</span>). 
	<span class="hover" title="Title of chapter">Natural reactions and strategies</span>. In 
	<span class="hover" title="Editor(s)">B. A. Brown &amp; C. Chan</span> (Eds.), 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Title of book">Principles of biology</span></em> 
	(<span class="hover" title="edition">2nd ed.</span>, 
	<span class="hover" title="pages of the chapter referred to">pp. 148&#45;189</span>). 
	<span class="hover" title="Place of publication">Washington, DC</span>: 
	<span class="hover" title="Publisher">Wilton</span>.
</blockquote>
